urlText: Major Event Buses operating for P!NK concert at Olympic Park
content:
Saturday 16 March
  • From 3.30pm till midnight, Sydney Olympic Park Major Event Buses will run for the P!NK concert at Accor Stadium.
  • Travel on the Major Event Buses is included in the cost of tickets to the P!NK concert only. Attendees do not need to tap on and off, simply show your concert ticket to the driver when boarding buses
  • Buses run every 5 to 20 minutes, subject to traffic conditions.
  • Note: buses will not leave Olympic Park until the concert has finished, expected from approximately 11pm. Passengers boarding services prior to the end of the show will need to wait until the concert has finished before the bus departs.
  • For more information on transport options to the event, see the P!NK concert event page.

All other stops remain the same.
